d</item></change><change n="meta.33467"><date>2009-03-20</date><respStmt><name>IDP</name></respStmt><item>Crosswalked to EpiDoc XML</item></change></revisionDesc></teiHeader><text><body><head lang="en"><date>IVspc</date>
<placeName cert="high">?</placeName></head><div lang="grc" part="N" type="edition"><div n="r" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/>τῷ δεσπότῃ μου τιμι<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ω</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">τ</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ά</unclear>τῳ καὶ ε<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ὐλ</unclear>α<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">βε</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">σ</supplied>τάτῳ 

    <lb n="2"/>Ἄπα Ἰωάννῃ <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">Η</unclear><gap extent="3" reason="lost" unit="character"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost"> Ἀ</supplied>βραὰμ 

    <lb n="3"/>ἐ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ν <expan>κ<ex cert="high">υρί</ex></expan>ῳ</supplied> <expan>Θ<ex cert="high">ε</ex></expan>ῷ χαίρειν. 

    <lb n="4"/>ὡ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ς</unclear> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">καὶ</unclear> πιστεύω ὅτι μ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">έλε</supplied>ται μου καὶ τοῦ οἴκου 

    <lb n="5"/><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">μου</unclear> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">σοι</unclear>, εὐχ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">αρ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ιστῶ</supplied> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">τ</unclear>ῇ σῇ θεοσεβείᾳ <sic>σου</sic>· 

    <lb n="6"/>οὕτω κ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">α</unclear>ί <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">σο</unclear>υ τὸ ἱερὸν <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">πρόσωπον</unclear> 

    <lb n="7"/>ἐν τῇ διανοίᾳ μου γίγνωσκέ με ἔχειν. 

    <lb n="8"/>προσαγορεύω σου τοιγαροῦν τὴν εὐλάβειάν 

    <lb n="9"/><sic>σου</sic> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">δι</unclear>ὰ τούτων μου <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">τ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ῶν γ</supplied>ραμμάτων, παρ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">α</unclear>-

    <lb n="10"/><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">κα</unclear>λῶν ὅπως μνημονεύῃς καὶ <choice><corr>ἐμοῦ</corr><sic>καμου</sic></choice> τοῦ σε 

    <lb n="11"/>προσκυνοῦντος καὶ <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">π</unclear>αντὸς τοῦ οἴκου μου 

    <lb n="12"/><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ἐν</unclear> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">αἷς</unclear> ἀναπέμπει<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ς</unclear> <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ἀεὶ</supplied> καὶ <choice><corr>καθ᾽</corr><sic>μεθ</sic></choice> ἡμέραν 

    <lb n="13"/>εὐχαῖς τῷ <subst><add place="inline">κυρίῳ</add><del rend="corrected">κωριω</del></subst> <choice><corr>σωτῆρι</corr><sic>σωτηρει</sic></choice> ἡμῶν. 

    <lb n="14"/>πέποιθα γὰρ ὡς διὰ τ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ῶ</unclear>ν <choice><corr>ἁγιωτάτων</corr><sic>αγιοτατων</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="15"/>σου εὐχῶν καὶ τ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">οῦ</unclear> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">κ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">α</supplied>μάτου τούτου 

    <lb n="16"/>ἐν ᾧ ἐσμ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ὲν</unclear> ἐ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">λευθ</unclear>ερωθῆναι καὶ 

    <lb n="17"/>ἐπανελθεῖν πρὸς <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ὑ</supplied>μᾶς. <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">λ</unclear>οιπόν, <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">δέ</unclear>σπο-

    <lb n="18"/>τα, ἀληθῶς Θεο<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ῦ</unclear> ἄνθρωπε, 

    <lb n="19"/>καταξίωσον <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ἐ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ν</supplied> μνήμαι<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ς</unclear> ἔχειν 

    <lb n="20"/>ἡμᾶς. προσαγ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">όρ</unclear>ευε παρ᾽ ἐμοῦ 

    <lb n="21"/>πάντας τοὺς <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">σὺν</supplied> σοὶ κάμνοντας 

    <lb n="22"/>ἀδελφούς. ὁ παντοκράτωρ 

    <lb n="23"/>Θε<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ὸς</unclear> διαφυ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">λ</unclear>άξῃ σε ἐπὶ 

    <lb n="24"/>πολ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ὺ</unclear>ν χρ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">όνο</unclear>ν ἡμῖν 

    <lb n="25"/>τοῖς ἁ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">μ</unclear>αρ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">τωλ</unclear>οῖς, ἵνα 

    <lb n="26"/><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">διὰ</unclear> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">τῶν</unclear> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">σῶν</unclear> <choice><corr>ἁγιωτάτων</corr><sic><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">αγιοτατων</unclear></sic></choice> 

    <lb n="27"/><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">εὐ</unclear>χ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ῶν</unclear> <choice><corr>διασωθῶμεν</corr><sic>δ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ιασω</unclear>σθωμεν</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="28"/>διὰ τ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">οῦ</unclear> βί<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ου</unclear>. 
</ab></div><div n="v" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="29"/>τῷ δεσπότῃ μου τιμιωτάτῳ καὶ εὐλαβ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">εστάτῳ Ἄπα Ἰωάννῃ</supplied>. </ab></div></div><div n="meta.33467" part="N" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.33467" part="N" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="400" notBefore="376" type="textDate">spätes IV</date></p></div><div n="meta.33467" part="N" subtype="general" type="commentary"><p>Gehört zum Archiv des Apa Johannes. Vgl. APF 40, 1994, S. 82-84. Zum Ort und zur Datierung vgl. BL X, S. 85 mit  BASP 32, 1995, S. 190 -  192 (Datierung gegen BL IX, S. 107).</p></div><div n="meta.33467" part="N" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl><bibl subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Herm.</title><biblScope type="numbers">8</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">33467</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP"><series>0134</series>; ; <biblScope type="numbers">8</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0134;;8" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.33467" part="N" subtype="corrections" type="bibliography"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><listBibl><bibl type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">IX</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">107</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">X</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">85</biblScope></bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.33467" part="N" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.33467" part="N" subtype="otherPublications" type="bibliography"><head>Andere Publikationen</head><listBibl><bibl subtype="other" type="publication">Naldini, Cristianesimo 83</bibl><bibl subtype="other" type="publication">Tibiletti, Lettere private 33</bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.33467" part="N" subtype="translations" type="bibliography"><head>Übersetzunge